    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nSometimes commits in the confirmation window are shown twice like:\n\\> A\n\\> B\n\\> A\n\\> B\n\n<img width=\"1508\" height=\"316\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e1c56fd9-22d5-449f-8aa8-b8d7a7bb5538\" />\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nHave nvim-treesitter installed (version: 6620ae1c44dfa8623b22d0cbf873a9e8d073b849).\nCurrent HEAD commit for nvim-treesitter is 7caec274fd19c12b55902a5b795100d21531391f , I don't know if it's reproducible with another commit added.\n\nnvim --clean\n:lua vim.pack.update()\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nEvery commit is shown only once\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.12.0-dev-2721+g9383a096eb\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nn/a\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacOS Tahoe 26.3.1 (25D2128) arm64\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nGhostty 1.3.2-main+bebca8466\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-ghostty\n\n### Installation\n\nbuilt from source",
